{"tid":2094661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【初選論壇醜態收集箱】","createTime":"2020-07-04T22:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T10:24:19.000Z","uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2244ccafda0e3fbc1c9221e58c9cd5b1d606c89f","tid":2094661,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T22:12:32.000Z","msg":"睇左少少初選<br />\n根本無人講國安法 <br />\n個個都係度奶35+奶議席<br />\n言論驚俾人ＤＱ驚撚過閪咁<br />\n睇到反胃<br />\n<br />\n因為本人仲未得閒睇哂咁多場初選<br />\n呢個post目的係想收集初選各大政治家偉論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下會再開個ＰＯ或用ｐｉｎ做個整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先拋磚引玉啦<br />\n頭先睇到有ＰＯ討論呢位政治家<br />\n忍唔住整左個ｇｉｆ<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主持問：你點睇新一代抗爭者　以攬炒為前提進入議會呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSOE6Cz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSOE6Cz.gif&h=24e5344c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/rk1blx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Frk1blx&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=d1e9b1aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/rk1blx</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n=============================<br />\nＦＹＩ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200622/4QFCMT7ADVG6PKAMIJ4XGDM4PI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200622%2F4QFCMT7ADVG6PKAMIJ4XGDM4PI%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=ac8be3cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200622%2F4QFCMT7ADVG6PKAMIJ4XGDM4PI%2F&h=09194799\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200622/4QFCMT7ADVG6PKAMIJ4XGDM4PI/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKKH471.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKKH471.png&h=b46f91fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡單講又要參選 又要係國安法下縮<br />\n俾你入到議會話知你50+ <br />\n根本係永續社運 係維穩 係打工 係食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係你就堂堂正正支持國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n縮就同中間派希望聯盟 同袁彌昌無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6359459709aba53be149b11e4901e015d472d8de","tid":2094661,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T22:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67831fca42872135c64c43b9d27fe4e088c811db","tid":2094661,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T22:48:10.000Z","msg":"唔要攬炒<br />\n要勝利!!!<br />\n<br />\nplease define勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答: 勝利=不被DQ進入立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a715ff5044bbbea29786390cac6ff130fe707716","tid":2094661,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T22:49:45.000Z","msg":"仲有無更多例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好有片有link有埋時間可供欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2733458025dee9d72eeb7e53f14108288df2f9a1","tid":2094661,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T22:56:07.000Z","msg":"仆街錯別字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係付出 唔係負出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c23a71ba499f147c1ce5d3ce5591c28734e97b","tid":2094661,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T23:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a3155357b1335cff997082d7e52ff6a879be66","tid":2094661,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T23:21:25.000Z","msg":"咁過癮既<br />\n個p